<p>HWAET is a creative company founded by James Carney and Brice Stratford.

We develop television and film rooted in history and place. Working collaboratively with local communities, historians, craftspeople and cultural organisations, we create productions with strong distictive voices and lasting connections to the places from which they emerged.
